The endpoint5 in the provided PrintRequestController corresponds to the POST endpoint at /consumer/budget. Its method signature is calcBudgetForPrintRequest(HttpServletRequest request, Principal principal, @RequestPart("printRequest") String requestJSON). This endpoint expects a multipart/form-data request containing:
- A mandatory part named "printRequest" which carries a JSON payload as a string (the budget calculation request).
- Optional file parts (any number of uploaded files) that are processed by the endpoint to be associated with the print request.

Given Swagger 2.0 conventions for multipart/form-data, the parameter objects should reflect these parts:
- printRequest as a formData parameter of type string (required)
- files as one or more formData parameters of type file (optional)
